full_text: I've been working with the awesome new data available through the #nflverse packages. I was curious about team formations used in different situations. Naturally, I started with the Seahawks. The increase in 1 RB, 2 TE formations on 1st and 10 in the last 2 seasons is interesting https://t.co/ql6WyDCnov

Every day until the season starts I am going to challenge myself to make something with the new nflreadr data related to the Bengals. This chart uses participation data to evaluate player usage week by week.  #nflverse #CincinnatiBengals #WhoDey https://t.co/cXhRU1x3or
